    "full_text": "SPECIAL PURPOSE FOR SALE\n\nSMUDGE CAR & DOG WASH KW\n\n6295 Templeton Gap Rd, Colorado Springs, CO 80923 COMMERCIAL\n\nPROPERTY OVERVIEW\nA well established automatic car wash and self-service dog\nwith in-house groomer. ts located near several other high\ntraffic businesses and is practically in the back yard of a\nvariety of housing communities. Smudge has been around\nsince 2005. This is a great opportunity for those looking for\nan established business.\n\nLOCATION OVERVIEW\nLocated in northern Colorado Springs, near North Powers\nBivd. and Dublin Blvd.\n\nTHE COLORADO DOG MAGAZINE\n\u201cStop by the Smudge Dog & Car Wash at 6295 Templeton\nGap Road on the way home and get your pooch and your\nvehicle all spruced up before heading out. Your dog will love\nthe bubble bath so you will really find it a unique business to\nvisit before you get on the road.\"\n\nCOLORADO SPRINGS STYLE MAGAZINE\n\n\u201cWhile there are many outlets where you can wash your dog,\nSmudge Dog Wash at powers and Dublin boulevards offers\na unique approach. Customers can wash their care and their\ndog at the same location, but not with the same wand.\nChopped off pickup beds serve as the washbasins and\naccommodate dogs of all sizes. Dogs can run around in an\noutdoor play park while their owners use the automated car\nwash and free vacuums.\u201c\n\nTHE GAZETTE\n\"Smudge a one-stop spot to clean up cars and pets\"\n\nBARRY B, BOUNDS // 720.221.1820 // bounds@kw.com\nkwcommercial.com",
