    "excerpt": "Asking $1,190,000 Established 1960 Price: Year BUSINESS DESCRIPTION 150\u2019 Touchless High Pressure Tunnel Wash Chief\u2019s Auto Wash presents a rare opportunity to acquire a long-established business and real estate offering at 4325 & 4345 Monticello Blvd., South Euclid, OH, priced at $1,190,000.",
    "full_text": "Asking $1,190,000 Established 1960\nPrice: Year:\n\nListing ID: 2455993 Listing provided by BizBuySell\n\nBUSINESS DESCRIPTION\n\n150\u2019 Touchless High Pressure Tunnel\nWash\n\nChief\u2019s Auto Wash presents a rare opportunity\nto acquire a long-established business and\nreal estate offering at 4325 & 4345 Monticello\nBlvd., South Euclid, OH, priced at $1,190,000.\nThis 65+ year successful operation is situated\non just over one acre with outstanding\nexposure, featuring approximately 322 feet of\nfrontage on Monticello Boulevard and traffic\ncounts of 20,000 vehicles per day. The\nproperty is strategically located directly down\nthe street from the approximately $300 million\nBelle Oaks Marketplace redevelopment,\nformerly Richmond Mall, enhancing long-term\nvisibility and growth potential.\n\nThe car wash operation includes a 150-foot\ntouchless high-pressure tunnel wash on a\nconveyor system with log chain and rollers,\nutilizing filtered reclaimed water for\noperational efficiency and reduced utility\ncosts. Wash components include an\nundercarriage bath, lambswool cloth curtains\n\nhttps://www.loopnet.com/biz/business-opportunity/successful-auto-wash-business-and-real-estate-with-high-visibility/2455993/\n\neee\n\n1/7/26, 8:59 PM\nPage 2 of 6",
