    "full_text": "Mike Shullman\n\nFrom: Ayman Sultan <Ayman,Sultan@matthews.com>\nSent: Monday, November 3, 2025 2:27 PM\n\nTo: Mike Shullman\n\nSubject: Newer Build Take 5 - Minneappolis MSA\n\nMike,\n\nHope you're doing well. | wanted to reach out and see if there was any interest in evaluating this former Take 5\noutside Minneapolis. | was telling you about this site when we were in Vegas actually. Pricing guidance is going to\nbe under 3M but if someone is able to come close to 2M the seller is going to be able to sell it off. We have offers\nbut speed to close is a priority here. The building opened as a ground up site in 2023 so figured I'd send over since\nit's tough to build in this market with a lack of existing inventory in this price range\n\nDriven Brands opened the store in 2023 and a local self-serve operator purchased it last year and would like to sell\nit before year end to transition funds into NNN. The buitding is in great shape with all the plumbing and other\nfactors being repaired when Take 5 closed it down and went through the winter months. This was part of Take 5's\n100s of properties being restructured - There is another tunnel down the street, and they're also interested in\npurchasing this site. The visibility to traffic is good but the accessibility is not the best on this one. The owner is a\nbit old school so there isn't too much data for financials especially since the site is still new in operating. Pricing is\ngoing to be under replacement costs and all offers would be considered depending on terms.\n\nCielo Car Wash (Former Take 5) - 4008 Deegan Ct, Monticello, MN 55362\n\nPricing Guidance: Being close to $2M can get a deat done. Quick closing preferred\nYear Built: 2022\n\nTake 5 opened in March'23 and stopped operating in October\u201923 - Opened again w/ new buyer in Q2 2025\nExpress\n\nPay Stations: 2\n\nPOS: DRB\n\nMembers: + 300 - 400\n\nVacs: = 16\n\nVac Equipment: VacuTec\n\nTunnel Equipment: MacNeil\n\nTunnel Length: + 125ft\n\nLot Size: 1.16 acres\n\nTake Care,\n\nAyman Sultan\nAssociate | Matthews\u2122 Car Wash Division\nDirect +1 623 887 96514 | Mobile +4 425 753 1211\n\nayman.sultan@matthews.com\nLicense No, SA695342000 (AZ}\n\nMATTHEWS\u201d\n\nClick Here For All Available Inventory\n4110 N Scottsdale Rd, Suite 100 | Scottsdale, AZ 85251",
