    "full_text": "'Kleen N Green Car Wash \n30 Perronette St \nBridgeport, CT \nFairfield County \n\n$1,100,000 includes property \n\nSELLING W MILFORD LOCATION \n\nFull service/exterior car wash on almost 1.5 acres. 80' tunnel with Econocraft equipment. Seller has \nowned the car wash for 9 years. Land appraised for $700K in 2011. Could easily convert to an express \nwash. Car wash established in 1964. \n\nTrailing 12 months as of June 2019 \nTunnel Sales: $318,594(27K cars) \nDetail: $51,884 \nStore Sales: $4,523 \n\nTotal Sales: $375,000",
